docs {
  # Update Budget
  
  Updates an existing budget.
  
  ## Path Parameters
  
  - `id` (required): Budget ID
  
  ## Request Body (all optional)
  
  - `amount`: New budget amount
  - `period`: Budget period (monthly, yearly)
}
